<section>
    <div class="block remove-bottom pt25">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <marquee direction="left"
                         behavior="alternate"
                         onmouseover="this.stop();"
                         onmouseout="this.start();">
                    <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kaushalpanjee&pcampaignid=web_share"
                       style="color:red;font-size:16px;text-decoration:none;"
                       target="_blank"
                       onmouseover="this.style.color='blue';"
                       onmouseout="this.style.color='red';">
                        <b>दीन दयाल उपाध्याय ग्रामीण कौशल योजना में निःशुल्क प्रशिक्षण के पंजीकरण हेतु यहाँ क्लिक करें (कौशल पंजी)</b>
                    </a>
                </marquee>
            </div>
        </div>
<div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <marquee direction="right"
                         behavior="alternate"
                         onmouseover="this.stop();"
                         onmouseout="this.start();">
                    <a href="https://lmsupsdm.com/lms/home"
                       style="color:red;font-size:16px;text-decoration:none;"
                       target="_blank"
                       onmouseover="this.style.color='blue';"
                       onmouseout="this.style.color='red';">
                        <b>ऑनलाइन प्रशिक्षण के लिए कौशल दिशा पोर्टल हेतु यहाँ क्लिक करें</b>
                    </a>
                </marquee>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="welcome-sec">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 col-lg-8 animate__animated animate__jackInTheBox animate__delay-2s">
                        <div class="welcome-secinfo">
                            <h2 class="font400 mNewFont">Welcome <br />To<br /> U.P. Skill Development Mission</h2>
                            <span>-----------------------</span>
                            <p>To Train all eligible youth in 14-35 age group in the trades of their preference,provide facilities for acquisition and upgradation of skills of the unskilled and semi skilled workforce,enabling Provision for the vulnerable section e.g. women, pwd and minorities. 30% targets are earmarked for women; 20% for minorities,provide trainings in NSQF (National Skills Qualifications Framework) compliant courses only.</p>
